frames.caption: A tall woman in a red blazer and black shorts stands confidently beside a shorter man in a white shirt and blue pants. They are positioned in front of a large airport window with a vibrant sunset sky and an airplane visible outside.

frames.description: The scene takes place in an airport terminal during sunset, with a focus on the contrasting heights of the two individuals. The woman exudes confidence and elegance, while the man appears to be in awe, creating a playful and lighthearted atmosphere.
